## Verification Plan

### Automated
- Dev server starts cleanly (`npm run dev`)
- API routes return correct HTTP status codes via browser network tab

### Manual
1. Admin creates a webinar with 2–3 questions → questions persist (check Supabase table)
2. Enrolled user opens the webinar → sees the questions form, can submit answers
3. User edits and re-submits an answer → answer is updated (upsert)
4. Admin/Faculty open the webinar → sees all user answers per question
5. Non-enrolled user opens the webinar → questions section is hidden or shows "Enroll to answer"

